I'm a fan.  I've traveled to Thailand and the staff is generally helpful in making recipes less authentic.  I keep forgetting NOT to order vegetarian pad thai.  Broccoli doesn't belong in that dish!  Other things are great.  My favorites are larb, fish cakes, and pumpkin curry.  My mother most loved duck red curry.  Everything is accurate level of spiciness.  Dine in or take out, it's a safe bet.

