I love Scramble.  It's the place I go when I need to do a fast business breakfast/lunch, want to sit with a novel and linger, or need to be fed fast because I just hiked North Mountain.  The food is great, there's something on the menu for everyone.  Love it.  Only reason I'm not giving 5 stars is sometimes I lose patience with new staff.  I've been a regular for a couple of years, so I know the menu better than they do.  Shame on me for impatience!

